Ok finished fury mastery, here are my numbers for fury 1 and 2.  I never had damage shield, MoK, etc so all data should be correct:<br>
<br>
Fury Mastery 1: 6524 cast, 597 crits = 9.15<br>
<br>
Fury Mastery 2: 6945 cast, 777 crits = 11.18<br>
