<br>
Is there a point at which the damage is random? Most of this thread talks about the frequency of the crits but what are the &quot;amplitudes&quot; per se?<br>
And how much does it change per skill level?<br>
<br>
If anyone can answer this, Id appreciate it. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
